    "lyrics": {
      "text": "O_ The-o-to--kos and Vir-gin, re-joice, O Mar-y, full of grace; the Lord is with thee. Bless-ed art thou a-mong wom-en, and bless-ed is the Fruit of thy womb; for thou hast borne the Sav-iour of our souls._____"
